          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How does a title case converter work?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "<p>A title case converter automatically capitalizes the first letter of each major word in your text while keeping minor grammatical words (such as articles, prepositions, and conjunctions) in lowercase, ensuring your headlines match standard formatting rules.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How do I use the upper case to lower case converter online?",
