            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "<p>To use the upper case to lower case converter, simply paste your text into the input field and select the lowercase output. The upper to lower case converter instantly formats all letters to lowercase. You can also use the lower case to upper case converter to do the reverse in one click.</p>"
          }
        },
