          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What is a sentence case converter?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "<p>A sentence case converter capitalizes the first letter of every sentence in your text block and converts the remaining characters to lowercase, making it highly useful for fixing raw, unformatted notes or poorly capitalized paragraphs.</p>"
