          "name": "Is this letter case converter secure for private text?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "<p>Yes. This cap case converter and proper case converter operates entirely in your browser using client-side JavaScript. None of the text you convert is ever sent to external servers, providing 100% data privacy.</p>"
